---
title: Hawaiian-Inspired Pork Burgers with Potato Wedges and Green Onion Aioli Dipping Sauce
description: Tender pork, juicy sweet pineapple and a zippy green onion aioli come together for the ultimate sammie! This  Hawaiian-inspired burger will be on the dinner table in no time!
